.SH NAME
fsl_dma_abort_stream \- tell ALSA that the DMA transfer has aborted
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" fsl_dma_abort_stream
.BI "(struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "substream" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

This function should be called by the ISR whenever the DMA controller
halts data transfer.
